  "keyFeatures": [
    "Facebook Login with OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect support",
    "Limited Login mode for iOS 14+ privacy compliance",
    "Content sharing via dialogs (links, photos, videos, camera effects)",
    "Graph API client for making authenticated requests to Facebook's API",
    "App Events analytics for tracking user actions and conversions",
    "Gaming Services: context dialogs, game requests, tournaments, media upload",
    "App Links support for deep linking and deferred deep linking",
    "Swift Package Manager, CocoaPods, and Carthage support",
    "In-App Purchase event tracking with StoreKit and StoreKit 2 APIs",
    "AEM (Aggregated Event Measurement) for privacy-preserving ad attribution"
  ],
